# {{name}}

Express + TypeScript + ESM backend scaffolded with [xpressify](https://www.npmjs.com/package/xpressify).

## Requirements

- Node.js >= 20

## Setup

```bash
npm install
cp .env.example .env
```

## Scripts

```bash
npm run dev     # start with auto-reload (tsx watch)
npm run build   # compile to dist/
npm start       # run the compiled build
```

## Project structure

```
src/
├── app.ts          Express app (cors, helmet, rate-limit, /health)
├── server.ts       entry point (dotenv + app.listen)
├── routes/         request routing
├── controllers/    request handlers
├── services/       business logic
├── middlewares/    custom Express middleware
└── utils/          shared helpers
```

## Adding components

```bash
npx xpressify g route users        # router + controller + service
npx xpressify g middleware auth    # typed middleware
npx xpressify g class src/models/User
```
